                      [
                        "Website Traffic",
                        "Conversion Rate",
                        "Line + Circle",
                        "Volume vs Quality"
                      ],
                      [
                        "Production Output",
                        "Defect Rate",
                        "Bars + Line",
                        "Quantity vs Quality"
                      ]
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "paragraph",
                    "text": "A common business pattern is: Volume-based metric as Bars, Efficiency-based metric as Line. This visually separates magnitude from performance quality."
                  }
