              {
                "id": "formatting",
                "title": "How Should You Format Dual-Axis Charts for Clarity?",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "paragraph",
                    "text": "Formatting determines whether a dual-axis chart builds trust or confusion."
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "checklist",
                    "items": [
                      {
                        "checked": true,
                        "text": "Clearly label both Y-axes"
